window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>There are three sides to every story: Yours. Mine. And the truth...</b> </p> <p>Max and Alissa have a fairy tale life - newlywed, madly in love and enviously rich. Then Max is brutally stabbed to death at their home and Alissa, miraculously, escapes with her life. But why was she spared? </p> <p>The hunt for the killer begins, uncovering a number of leads - was Max's incredible wealth the motive? Had his shady business practices finally caught up with him? Or was it a stalker with a dangerous obsession? </p> <p>Devoted friends rally around gentle, sweet Alissa as she is left to mourn the loss of her husband and pick up her life. But not everyone is who they seem...Deep-rooted jealousies, secrets and twisted love lie just beneath the surface, and not all fairy tales have a happy ending. </p> <p><i>Duplicity</i> is a suspenseful thriller from the bestselling author of <i>Look Behind You</i> and <i>Where the Memories Lie</i>. </p>"; 
